xsecurelock (1.3-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Upstream version 1.3
  * ./xsecurelock --help and --version.
  * Now with manpage.                                                              
  * Auth window is now a box in front of the saver.                                
  * Better slideshow support in saver_mpv.                                         
  * Configurable auth dialog colors.                                               
  * Improved SIGTERM/SIGCHLD handling; no more race that might kill other processes. 
  * Optional display of current date and time.
  * Optional force-grab feature to break other applications' grabs.
  * Support for custom hotkeys.                                                    
  * Support to play speaker sounds during auth flow.                               

 -- Rudolf Polzer <rpolzer@google.com>  Mon, 15 Apr 2019 07:06:34 -0700

xsecurelock (1.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Upstream version 1.1
  * Fix separator display logic.
  * Additional obscurer window.
  * Grab on root window.
  * Add window unmapper that allows xsecurelock to steal grabs (default: off).
  * Correctly parse xscreensaver preferences.
  * Use real time clock for auth timeout.
  * Only show "Processing..." if the last PAM action was a prompt.
  * Add keyboard layout switching shortcut to auth_pam_x11 module.
  * Add date and PID to log output.

 -- Markus Teich <mteich@google.com>  Mon, 17 Sep 2018 19:53:52 +0200

